divs: sighting details my camera was set up to take time lapse, one photo every minute. when reviewing later that night i saw this image in one frame. the location is 35 ave. and lower buckeye rd. in phoenix looking south over the estrella mnts. 9:50 am. i also have collected some anomalous fibers falling from the sky both in town and way out in the desert. i have examined the fibers under 20x magnification, ultraviolet light, and side by side with cotton and spider\cobwebs. it is some strange stuff. feel free to contact me by e-mail or phone after 4pm. *(wit's name and phone number removed--cms\sg)if you have any questions. the first photo is as taken and the other two are cropped and enlarged 2x with photo editor in picasa. i will send some pictures of the anomolous fibers in a second e-mail.
Summary: Anomolous light in time-lapse series of pictures
